    <item>
      <title>Why should I switch to Linux from Windows?</title>
      <link>https://christitus.com/linux-switch-video/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Oct 2018 17:59:04 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://christitus.com/linux-switch-video/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This will be the first article in a series of Linux articles, I am going over 6 reasons to switch to Linux and 1 big reason not to. Many people ask “Why should I switch to Linux from Windows?” and in this article below I break it down for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;pros&#34;&gt;Pros&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It’s Free – Tons of Free software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No big brother – Microsoft Telemetry reports on you!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stable – Can go months or even years before rebooting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Works on anything – Pretty much any piece of hard will run Linux.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Updates the way you WANT!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Virus/malware resistant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;cons&#34;&gt;Cons&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Windows only software
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Microsoft Office&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adobe Software Suite&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Specific Games&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;video-walkthrough&#34;&gt;Video Walkthrough&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s5QGZ-DBYGs&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://img.youtube.com/vi/s5QGZ-DBYGs/0.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;linuxswitch-yt&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
